tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cbl1665702769628.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cbl1665702769628.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cbl1665702769628.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cbl1665702769628\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Enable DDE Support\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface DDE support requires the <span class=\"ph filepath\">udde.dll</span> to be loaded when Uniface starts.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__context_w5799ab1b5b1_w5800ab1b5_w5801ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__p_d35504e1_d35505e1_d35506e1\">To enable DDE support:</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__li_d18206e1_d18207e1_d18208e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Set the <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fjy1665702674311.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fjy1665702674311.html\" title=\"Controls whether DDE support is available within a Uniface application.\">DDE</a> setting in the <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"crc1665702674239.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crc1665702674239.html\" title=\"The [udde] section controls the use of Dynamic Data Exchange (DDE) support from within a Uniface application.\">[udde]</a> section of your <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file to <code class=\"ph codeph\">On</code>.\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[udde]\nDDE=on</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__li_d18209e1_d18210e1_d18211e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Edit the application's assignment file to add the appropriate module to the <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"daw1665702678607.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/daw1665702678607.html\" title=\"Use the [USER_3GL] section of the assignment file to lists third-party components and Uniface 3GL extensions to be made available to Uniface.\">[USER_3GL]</a> section. Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/preload</span> setting. For example:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[USER_3GL]\nusyscom:/bin/udde.dll /preload </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__li_d18212e1_d18213e1_d18214e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__p_d35507e1_d35508e1_d35509e1\">Create a signature for the UDDE component. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zzx1665702678830.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zzx1665702678830.html\" title=\"Use the Signature Editor to create or modify component signatures. Signatures of Uniface components are automatically generated during compilation. Signatures of non-Uniface components can be created or imported.\">Define a Component Signature</a>\n</span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__li_d18215e1_d18216e1_d18217e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More Editors &gt; Signature</span></span>.\n </span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__li_d18218e1_d18219e1_d18220e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__p_d35510e1_d35511e1_d35512e1\">Set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Implementation</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code> and define the operations with no parameters.\n\n                        <img alt=\"Signature Editor showing UDDE signature including operations\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/uddesig.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__li_d18221e1_d18222e1_d18223e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__p_d35513e1_d35514e1_d35515e1\">Edit the details of each operation to remove the <var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var> prefix that Uniface automatically adds to the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Literal Name</span> of C implementations.\n                         <img alt=\"Signature Operations editor showing details of uddeExecute\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/uddeexecutesigprops.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__li_d18224e1_d18225e1_d18226e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Save and compile the signature.\n </span>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li></ol></section>\n<section class=\"section result body required-cleanup-multiple-ol-elements-in-topic-body\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__result_w5802ab1b5b5_w5803ab1b5_w5804ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cbl1665702769628__p_d35516e1_d35517e1_d35518e1\">Once UDDE is enabled, you can use Uniface as a UDDE client or server.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gkm1665702892640.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface as a DDE Client</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/izj1665702893142.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface as a DDE Server</a><p>When Uniface acts as a DDE server, the DDE link must be defined in the client application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526359\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526359\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Enable DDE Support Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Enable DDE Support Uniface DDE support requires the udde.dll to be loaded when Uniface starts. To enable DDE support: Set the DDE setting in the [udde] section of your .ini file to On . [udde] DDE=on Copy Edit the application's assignment file to add the appropriate module to the [USER_3GL] section. Use the /preload setting. For example: [USER_3GL] usyscom:/bin/udde.dll /preload Copy Create a signature for the UDDE component. For more information, see Define a Component Signature Choose More Editors > Signature . Set the Implementation to C and define the operations with no parameters. Edit the details of each operation to remove the ComponentName prefix that Uniface automatically adds to the Literal Name of C implementations. Save and compile the signature. Once UDDE is enabled, you can use Uniface as a UDDE client or server. Related Links Uniface as a DDE Client Uniface as a DDE Server When Uniface acts as a DDE server, the DDE link must be defined in the client application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}